Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,CORSAIR. Maritime risk forecasts for contested logistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Every MEU PMC routes through three of the top five piracy basins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,NGA ASAM gives you yesterday. CORSAIR gives you the next 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,60 by 60 KDE grid. Recency weighted. Seasonality corrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An LLM agent ingests the top five hotspots and recent attack\Nnarratives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It drafts a SIPR-format Maritime Intel Summary and structured\Nindicator board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Three clicks: theater, generate, drilldown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill into a hotspot — the three real incidents that produced the\Nforecast appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL — same code, now on-prem via the Inference Mesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,IL5 / IL6 ready. ReBAC. Zero data movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,CORSAIR. Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Powered by Kamiwaza.
